high_descs: Turn left and walk up to the stove.
Pick up the metal pan off of the back left burner of the stove.
Turn right and begin walking to the sink, then hang a right and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and put the metal pan inside on the middle shelf, then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge door and take out the metal pan, then close the door again.
Turn left and begin walking across the room, then turn left and walk up to the stove.
Put the chilled metal pan on the front right burner of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled metal pan on the stove.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the stove.
Pick up the pan from the stove.
Turn right, then right again and take the pan to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the pan inside and then take it out again.
Turn left and walk back to the stove with the pan.
Set the pan on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Chill the pan and put it back on the stove.

high_descs: Turn left, go forward, then turn left to face the oven.
Pick up the pan on top of the oven.
Turn right, go forward, then turn right and go to the fridge.
Chill the pan inside of the fridge.
Turn left, go forward, turn left, then go forward and return to the oven.
Put the pan on top of the oven, on the front left range.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan on the oven.
